quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  6,69,Iwo amene amaopa Mulungu alibe udindo pa iwo koma kungowakumbutsa kuti apewe kunyoza
  6,70,"Apewe iwo amene amasandutsa chipembedzo chawo kukhala masewera kapena nthabwala ndipo asokonezeka ndi zokoma za moyo wa dziko lapansi. Koma achenjeze ndi ilo kuti ungadzaonongeke mzimu wawo chifukwa cha zimene udachita pamene siudzakhala ndi wousamalira kapena kuwuteteza kupatula Mulungu, ndipo ngakhale iwo apereka chuma chopepesera, sichidzalandiridwa konse. Otere ndiwo amene aonongedwa chifukwa cha zimene anachita. Iwo adzalandira zakumwa zowira ndi chilango chowawa chifukwa cha zinthu zimene sadakhulupirire"
  6,71,"Nena, “Kodi ife tizipembedza ena powonjezera pa Mulungu amene sangathe kutithandiza kapena kutiwononga ndipo kodi ife tibwerere m’mbuyo pamene Mulungu watitsogolera? Monga ngati munthu amene alodzedwa ndi Satana, kumangoyenda uku ndi uku ngakhale kuti abwenzi ake ali kumuitana kuti atsatire njira yoyenera, ponena: Bwerani kuno?” Nena, “Ndithudi utsogoleri wa Mulungu ndiwo utsogoleri weniweni ndipo Ife talamulidwa kugonjera Mulungu Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”"
  6,72,"Ndi kuti muzipemphera moyenera, kumvera Mulungu ndi kumuopa Iye ndipo ndi kwa Iye kumene nonse mudzasonkhanitsidwa"
  6,73,"Iye ndiye amene adalenga kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi mwachoonadi ndipo patsikuli Iye adzati: “Khala” ndipo chidzakhala. Liwu lake ndi loonadi. Wake udzakhala Ufumu pa tsiku limene lipenga lidzaombedwa. Iye amadziwa zonse zosaoneka ndi zooneka. Iye ndi wanzeru ndi wodziwa zinthu zonse"